t-accordion-panel-inner light-bg">
<p id=3D"paragraph-c426ee3" class=3D"paragraph-cea9327">CPM stands for =E2=
=80=9Ccost for 1,000 impressions.=E2=80=9D It is the price you pay for ever=
y 1,000 your content is viewed, regardless of whether that content gets cli=
cked or not.</p>
