ccordion-panel-inner light-bg">
<p id=3D"paragraph-c5f12b7" class=3D"paragraph-c613776">You can calculate C=
PM using the following formula: <br><br><strong>CPM =3D (Total Cost / Numbe=
r of Impressions) x 1,000</strong></p>
</div></div></div>



