-accordion-panel-inner light-bg">
<p id=3D"paragraph-c30ba73" class=3D"paragraph-cc74978">A good average CPM =
will depend on the size and reach of your creators, their industry or niche=
, and the overall goals of your campaign. But as a general rule, influencer=
 marketers should strive for about a $10 CPM.</p>
